        private static boolean isDominant(boolean _a1,
                                  boolean _a2)
        Returns whether this trait is a dominant trait or recessive
        If dominant, trait will be displayed with just one allele being set to true
        If recessive, trait will only be displayed if both alleles are set to false
        Parameters:
        _a1 - the first allele
        _a2 - the second allele
        Returns:
        true if one or both alleles are true (a1 & a2), false otherwise
